beer.beer_description:
Yep, more and more IPAs! We'll strap you down to a chair and pump you with tons of different hop varieties, until you will learn to love them all!

Shock Therapy, our ever-changing IPA series will give you jolts and shivers with each new version.

This one was brewed using truckloads of Sorachi Ace hops.

Contains barley malt, wheat malt, oat flakes and hops.
